 &lt;h1 id=&#34;Data-Type&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#Data-Type&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;Data Type&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Data Type&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;Easy&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#Easy&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;Easy&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Easy&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;problems_problem_content__Xm_eO&#34;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-size:18px&#34;&gt;Geek is learning a new programming language. As data type forms the most fundamental part of a language, Geek is learning them with focus and needs your help. Given a data type, help Geek in finding the size of it in byte.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-size:18px&#34;&gt;Data Type - &lt;strong&gt;Character, Integer, Long, Float and Double&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

