&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-size:18px&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Task:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-size:18px&#34;&gt;Complete the function &lt;strong&gt;dataTypeSize()&lt;/strong&gt; which takes a string as input and returns&amp;nbsp;the size of the data type represented by the given string in byte unit.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
